The techniques used in the paper involve matrix analysis and union bounds, which are common tools in theoretical computer science. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
